``` ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} library(hexbin) library(ggplot2) library(dplyr) ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` Adjuntando el paquete: 'dplyr' ``` ::: ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` The following objects are masked from 'package:stats': filter, lag ``` ::: ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` The following objects are masked from 'package:base': intersect, setdiff, setequal, union ``` ::: ```{.r .cell-code} library(sf) ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` Linking to GEOS 3.13.1, GDAL 3.11.4, PROJ 9.7.0; sf_use_s2() is TRUE ``` ::: :::
